tika.dc.description: In this remarkable story collection, ordinary people just like you recount miraculous and astounding answers to prayer. This book will strengthen your faith and inspire you to believe that God can and does answer our most seemingly impossible prayers, fulfilling our deepest needs and biggest dreams in ways we could never imagine.
